title: 820-3437 - dead with U8130
message:
Clean logic board, no oxidation, perfect!

I checked the main voltages, RTC and PCH. Only the PM_RSMRST_L 0v. I changed the U8130 three times and same problem.

If I don't put the U8130 on, it turns on!

title: 820-3437 - dead with U8130
message: Post all U8130 voltages; when in place, of course.

title: 820-3437 - dead with U8130
message:
3V3_S5 seems to be low, as 3V3_SUS too.
U8130 expects 3.07V at pin 2, in order to release PM_RSMRST_L.
